models.name: GRACE BARMORE
models.emailBody:
Hope you’re well! I wanted to introduce to you our new face model Grace Barmore. She recently turned 18, is 5’8” and based in Los Angeles.

Grace is a professional hip-hop dancer with a strong work ethic. Below is a link to her new digitals and portfolio. I'd love to set up a meeting to formally introduce you and connect.

https://whitecrossmanagement.mediaslide.com/package/view/858/c9b2e40e/1280/91520905
